room_title: Escape room "The Mummy's Curse" by Mystery Room Houston in Houston
review: Went here with my best friend and I have to say it was a freaking blast. Even though it was just me and him we enjoyed ourselves. The crew there was really awesome.

room_title: Escape room "The Mummy's Curse" by Mystery Room Houston in Houston
review: Great place! Great and fun employees! We did the Mummy room and it had us all puzzled!

room_title: Escape room "The Mummy's Curse" by Mystery Room Houston in Houston
review: My daughter and her friends had an amazing and exciting time. They did the Mummy's Curse room. They had so much fun that they wanted to do another room. The host (Rainbow) was very cool and nice too. We are definitely coming back!
